</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>PSA</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">—甲方对潜在供应商的评定流程；</span><span style="font-size:13px">Potential Supplier Assessment procedure of Party A to supplier </span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>TA</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">—甲方对供应商的技术评价流程；</span><span style="font-size:13px">Technology Assessment procedure of Party A to supplier </span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 47px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">溢出支付法—甲方对供应商货款的支付流程。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Overflow Payment method – Procedure of supplier payment for goods of Party A</span>
</p>
<p style="line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px;font-family:黑体">二、甲乙双方的责任</span> <span style="font-size:13px">Responsibility of Party A&amp;B</span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">1</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、严格遵守国家和地方所有适用的法律法规以及惩治腐败、廉洁诚信的规定、以及本协议的约定。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Strictly follow all national and regional applicable laws and regulations, provisions of combating corruption and being integrity and rules in the agreement.</span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">2</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">严格执行双方所签订的合同</span><span style="font-size:13px">/</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">协议文件，自觉按合同</span><span style="font-size:13px">/</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">协议办事。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Strictly enforce the contract/ agreement <span>&nbsp;</span>signed by both parties and act consciously based on the contract / agreement . </span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">3</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、建立健全廉政制度，开展廉洁诚信教育，监督并查处违法违纪行为。</span><span style="font-size: 13px">Establish and perfect incorrupt government, carry out honesty and integrity education, supervise, investigate and deal with any acts or behaviors that violate law and discipline. </span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">4</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、发现对方在业务活动中有违法、违规、违纪的行为，或者发现对方严重违反本协议条款的行为，有向其纪检监察部门或上级有关部门举报、建议给予处理并要求告知处理结果的权利。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Either party may be entitled to report to the other party’s discipline inspection and supervision department or superior authorities, suggest disposal and request the notification of disposal result when the other party’s act or behavior is found to break any law, regulation or discipline during business activity or severely violate any term of the agreement.</span>
</p>
<p style="line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px;font-family:黑体">三、甲方责任</span> <span style="font-size:13px">Responsibility of Party A</span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">1</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、严格遵守公平、公正、公开执行向乙方公布和承诺的采购流程（</span><span style="font-size:13px">QPST</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、</span><span style="font-size:13px">PSA</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、</span><span style="font-size:13px">TA</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、</span><span style="font-size:13px">IPTV</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">溢出支付法等）和相关规定；国家规定的公开招投标项目必须公开招投标，不采取化整为零等方式规避招投标。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Strictly follow the spirit of fairness, justice, openness and execute the purchase process (QPST, PSA, TA, IPTV, Overflow payment method etc.) and related rules that are published and committed to Party B. The public bidding project that is defined by national regulation shall be bidden in public and is forbidden to avoid bidding by </span><span style="font-size:13px;color:black">splitting project into smaller ones</span><span style="font-size:13px">.</span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">2</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、招投标全过程保守乙方投标内容秘密，不向任何投标方泄露与招投标相关的任何信息，也不透露投标方的商业秘密，不对投标方做任何承诺；不得影响、诱导和要求招投标过程依照自己的意见进行评审，坚决执行公开的招标规定和承诺。</span><span style="font-size:13px">During bidding and tendering process, the confidential information of bidding content of Party B shall be guaranteed. Neither reveal the bidding information to any bidders, disclose any business secret of bidders nor make promise to any bidders; The process shall not be impact, induced or required to be assessed based on one ‘own opinion. Strictly follow the opening bidding rules and commitment.</span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">3</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、经</span><span style="font-size:13px">JPC</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">确认的采购合同，不得向与采购合同无关的人员和第三方泄露采购合同的任何内容。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Never reveal the content of purchase contract confirmed by JPC to the irrelevant personnel or the third party. </span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">4</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、严格执行在</span><span style="font-size:13px">QPST</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">（质量、价格、服务、技术）对供应商评价、评级等方面公布的流程，不得存在排他性、倾向性和歧视性行为。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Strictly execute the published process of supplier evaluation and rating related on QPST (Quality, Price, Service and Technology). Any exclusive, tendentious and discriminatory behaviors are not allowed.</span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">5</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、禁止甲方人员及其</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">“</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">特定关系人</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">”</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">有关联的供应商参与招投标。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Any supplier who is relevant to the Party A and the specific relevant party of Party A is forbidden to participate in the bidding and tendering.</span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">6</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、乙方知晓并同意根据甲方的相关规定，甲方人员不得私自接待乙方及其工作人员对甲乙双方采购业务相关事项的询访，不得私自为乙方的业务开展提供甲方规定以外的任何便利。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Party B acknowledges and agrees that pursuant to Party A</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">’</span><span style="font-size:13px">s own policy, Party A</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">’</span><span style="font-size:13px">s personnel </span><span style="font-size:13px">cannot entertain Party B or accept the inquiry related to the purchase business of both parties in privacy from Party B or its personnel or provide any convenience beyond Party A’s policy.</span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">7</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、乙方知晓并同意根据甲方的相关规定，甲方人员及其</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">“</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">特定关系人</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">”</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">不得在乙方兼职、投资、参股或以其他名义从乙方获取兼职工资、红利及其他各种形式的报酬；不得向乙方及其工作人员要求参与或影响乙方的采购业务等相关的经济活动。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Party B acknowledges and agrees that pursuant to Party A</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">’</span><span style="font-size:13px">s own policy, </span><span style="font-size:13px">personnel of Party A and specific relevant party are forbidden to take part-time job, invest, join stock, or obtain salary of part time job, bonus and all kinds of payment from Party B or request participation in or affect Party B’s purchase business or the related economy activity. </span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">8</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、乙方知晓并同意根据甲方的相关规定，甲方人员不得利用职权或职务之便索取或收受乙方财物，以及其他不正当利益；不得向乙方报销应由甲方或者甲方工作人员个人支付的费用，不得接受乙方及其工作人员以任何名义赠送的</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">现金或其他有价之物</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">，难以拒收的，要及时上交甲方纪委。</span><span style="font-size: 13px">Party B acknowledges and agrees that pursuant to Party A</span><span style="font-size: 13px;font-family:宋体">’</span><span style="font-size:13px">s own policy, Party A</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">’</span><span style="font-size:13px">s personnel </span><span style="font-size:13px">cannot claim for or accept the goods or any other illegitimate profits from Party B by taking the advantage of duty convenience, or claim any expense reimbursement from Party B which shall by paid by Party A or personnel of Party A, or receive cash or other<span>&nbsp; </span>valuable items from Party B or personnel of Party B. Party A should turn in Party A’s Discipline Inspection Commission if it’s difficult to refuse.</span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">9</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、乙方知晓并同意根据甲方的相关规定，甲方人员不得参加乙方及其工作人员组织的可能对公正执行业务有影响的宴请、娱乐和旅游等一切高消费活动，不得要求或者接受乙方及其工作人员为其住房装修、婚丧嫁娶、家属子女的就业以及出国等提供的便利。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Party B acknowledges and agrees that pursuant to Party A</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">’</span><span style="font-size:13px">s own policy, Party A</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">’</span><span style="font-size:13px">s personnel </span><span style="font-size:13px">cannot participate in the dinners or banquets, entertainment or tour or any other high-value consumption which are organized by Party B and their personnel and may impact fair business execution. Party A should not claim for or accept the convenience providing for housing decoration, wedding or funerals, employment or going abroad of own relatives or offspring from Party B or their personnel.</span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">10</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、保证</span><span style="font-size:13px">IPTV</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">流程和相关人员的公正性，准确评定销后故障模式和故障数，使乙方对销后赔偿合理化。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Guarantee the impartiality of IPTV procedure and relevant personnel; Make accurate judgment of after sales failure mode and failure quantity so as to ensure the contra compensation rationalization with Party B.</span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">11</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、本着“伙伴”关系，在与乙方业务往来中，建立平等、友好、公平、公正、公开的关系，杜绝</span><span style="font-size: 13px;font-family:宋体">甲方人员</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">对乙方的居高临下、歧视、刁难等恶劣行为。</span><span style="font-size:13px">In the spirit of “partnership”, establish equal, friendly, fair, justice and opening relationship with Party B during business contact and prevent any behaviors like condescending attitude, discrimination and obstruction to Party B. </span>
</p>
<p style="text-indent: 27px; line-height: 1.5em;">
    <span style="font-size:13px">12</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、建立举报投诉渠道，如有甲方人员违反本协议条款或向乙方索取不正当利益的，乙方可向甲方纪检监察部门如实进行举报投诉。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Set up report and complaint channel. Party B may report and complain truthfully to the discipline inspection and supervision department of Party A if personnel of Party A are found to have the acts of violation of terms of the agreement or claiming illegitimate profits from Party B.</span>
</p>
